006package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.model;
007
008import gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.core.datatype.IDataTypeAdapter;
009
010import edu.umd.cs.findbugs.annotations.NonNull;
011
012/**
013 * This marker interface identifies Metaschema definition types that have
014 * associated values (i.e., field, flag).
015 */
016public interface IValuedDefinition extends IDefinition {
017  /**
018   * Retrieves the data type of the definition's value.
019   *
020   * @return the data type
021   */
022  @NonNull
023  IDataTypeAdapter<?> getJavaTypeAdapter();
024}
